I want to first of all thank Ra5|<it for coming up with the idea of making a map based upon Takeshsis Castle's Honeycomb maze.  This may not be perfect but its alright.

In short its a fun map to play, it contains a gg version suitable for Gun Game and can be challenging even with the radar.  Have fun guys.

The radar isn't working properly, it repeats itself, if anyone knows why contact me.  Everything is embedded in BSP.
